{
  "name": "RPlog_Han_s_Nightmares",
  "title": "A Window on the Dream",
  "summary": "Back in the suite Han Solo shares with Princess Leia, Luke offers to use the Force to help his sleepless friend confront the nightmares that have plagued him since his Imperial imprisonment, promising only to lend clarity rather than intrude. As Han lies on the couch and Luke sinks into a guiding trance, Leia secretly watches from a cracked bedroom door, her concern for her husband bleeding through the Force to her brother. Shielded within a protective sphere of Luke's making, Han relives the dream in vivid fragments: the Noghri's torture, Grathix's coercion to run Kessel, the loss of the Falcon and his ability to fly, and finally the horror of his carbonized friends and Chewbacca's severed head. Han jolts awake, shaken but freed of the immediate fear, and Luke withdraws to give him peace. Drawn by an awareness that something has changed, Han stumbles into the bedroom and gathers a sleepless Leia into his arms, the couple finding rest together as Luke quietly assures Threepio that both will be fine.",
